rComments: Absolutely no purpose of going to class. She literally read everything off the slides.  Rude when dealing with concerns and questions from students. Made us write our name and student id every time before asking a question. If it wasn't for a prereq, would definitely not take this course!!

The prof is monotone and sounds like a computer automated voice system.... The exams were literally the lecture slides copy and paste onto the final word for word. Its a must to memorize the slides word for word to pass the exam.  She is rude and impatient when you go to her office hours.
